headline.main: Plans for Slain Firefighting Crew's Station in the Works
headline.print_headline: Plans for Slain Firefighting Crew's Station in the Works

lead_paragraph: Prescott residents are trying to come up with a plan to save a fire station that housed 19 firefighters who died in a 2013 wildfire before the city decides to sell the building.
